quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  68,43,"Ka b…õ nina ba tiŇčgbani ni, ka filiŇč Ňčari ba, achiika! B…õ daa ny…õla b…õ ni boondi shőĶba (Dunia puuni) ni b…õ ti niŇč suzuuda, ka b…õ ny…õla ban mali alaafee (ka za…£isi li)"
  68,44,"Dinzu…£u (yaa nyini Annabi)! ChőĶli Ma (Mani Naawuni) ni ninvu…£u so Ňčun labsi yőĶlt…Ē…£a (Alkur‚Äôaani) Ňč…Ē maa  íiri, Ni baalim, Ti (Tinim‚Äô Naawuni) ni gbaai ba lu…£ushőĶli polo b…õ ni b…õ mi"
  68,45,"Yaha! N (Mani Naawuni) na…£isiri mi n-tiri ba, achiika! N nabiőĶri ny…õla din kpőĶma"
  68,46,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Bee a b…Ēhiri ba la sanyo‚Äô shőĶli, ka dinzu…£u ch…õ ka samli maa niŇč timsim n-ti ba"
